<subSubSection lastPageId="3" lastPageNumber="96" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="2.[843,1494,1673,1955]" lastBlockId="3.[103,753,281,402]" lastPageId="3" lastPageNumber="96" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">
Under 
<treatmentCitation author="Hassler" page="68" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" year="1910">
<taxonomicName authority=", HASSLER (1910: 68)" authorityName=", HASSLER" authorityPageNumber="68" authorityYear="1910" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="longiflorum" variety="emarginatum">
<emphasis box="[955,1112,1673,1697]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">B. longiflorum</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis box="[1164,1314,1673,1697]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">emarginatum,</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="HASSLER" firstAuthor="HASSLER" page="68" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" pagination="66 - 71" refId="ref6666" refString="HASSLER, E. (1910). Ex herbario Hassleriano: Novitates paraguarienses. V. Bombacaceae. Repert. Spec. Nov. Regni Veg. 8: 66 - 71." type="journal article" year="1910">HASSLER (1910: 68)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
</treatmentCitation>
accommodated 
<taxonomicName box="[1053,1401,1705,1729]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" form="multifoliolatum" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="form" species="longiflorum">
<emphasis box="[1053,1209,1705,1729]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">B. longiflorum</emphasis>
f. 
<emphasis box="[1237,1401,1705,1729]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">multifoliolatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a different taxon from 
<taxonomicName authority="(R. E. Fr.) Hassl." authorityName="Hassl." baseAuthorityName="R. E. Fr." box="[1037,1494,1737,1761]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" form="elegans" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="form" species="longiflorum">
<emphasis box="[1037,1194,1737,1761]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">B. longiflorum</emphasis>
f. 
<emphasis box="[1224,1306,1737,1761]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">elegans</emphasis>
(R. E. Fr.) Hassl.
</taxonomicName>
(÷ 
<taxonomicName authority="R. E. Fr." authorityName="R. E. Fr. In" authorityYear="2014" box="[877,1087,1769,1793]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="elegans">
<emphasis box="[877,990,1769,1793]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">B. elegans</emphasis>
R. E. Fr.
</taxonomicName>
). However, Hassler did not designate a 
<typeStatus box="[863,958,1802,1826]" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">holotype</typeStatus>
for 
<taxonomicName authorityName=", HASSLER" authorityYear="1910" box="[1005,1196,1802,1826]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="longiflorum" variety="emarginatum">
var. 
<emphasis box="[1052,1196,1802,1826]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">emarginatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Types of the names of the two forms published by him (see under their names) are 
<typeStatus pageId="2" pageNumber="95">syntypes</typeStatus>
of this variety. We choose as 
<typeStatus box="[1232,1332,1866,1890]" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">lectotype</typeStatus>
of this 
<taxonomicName pageId="2" pageNumber="95" rank="variety" variety="the">variety the</taxonomicName>
specimen that is also the 
<typeStatus box="[1169,1267,1899,1923]" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" form="multifoliolatum" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="form" species="longiflorum">
<emphasis box="[1306,1469,1899,1923]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">B. longiflorum</emphasis>
f. 
<emphasis box="[843,1009,1931,1955]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">multifoliolatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as it allows a clear application of the present name according to Hassler’s concept. The 
<typeStatus box="[582,669,281,305]" pageId="3" pageNumber="96">syntype</typeStatus>
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="96">Malme s.n.</emphasis>
[SR11279] is also the 
<typeStatus box="[398,501,313,337]" pageId="3" pageNumber="96">lectotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="R. E. Fr. In" authorityYear="2014" box="[540,656,313,337]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="3" pageNumber="96" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="elegans">
<emphasis box="[540,656,313,337]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="96">B. elegans</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and the 
<typeStatus box="[103,190,346,370]" pageId="3" pageNumber="96">syntype</typeStatus>
<emphasis box="[198,322,346,370]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="96">Malme s.n.</emphasis>
[S10-38650] is also epitype of 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="96">
<taxonomicName authorityName="R. E. Fr. In" authorityYear="2014" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="3" pageNumber="96" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="elegans">B. elegans</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
